                </div>
                <div class="left-about-img">
                    <img src="./images/about-image1.jpg" alt="Jazzy man">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faux-border">a</div>
            <div>
                <div class="right-about-img">
                    <img src="./images/about-image2.jpg" alt="Hands in shape of heart">
                </div>
                <div class="right-about">
                    <h3>A Little About You</h3>
                    <p>(List of how you can help support local musicians or how you can join the catalog)Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Iste neque sed omnis beatae at excepturi adipisci suscipit tempore magni totam animi quam repudiandae, consequatur obcaecati pariatur ut similique maxime veniam.</p>
                </div>  
            </div>  
        </div>
    </section>
    {{> footer-and-scripts}}
</body>
</html>